<body>
    <%- include("partials/navbar") %>

    <div class="heading-picture">
        <img src="images/picture5.jpg" alt="">
        <h1 class="heading"><span style="color: white;"> SCHOOL </span><span style="color: blue;">ADMISSION</span></h1>
    </div>
    
    <section id="admission">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4 admission-policy">
                <h3>ADMISSION POLICY</h3>
                <p>Students are admitted into the JSS1 and SSS1 classes through the annual entrance examination. All applicants must pay a non-refundable application fee and complete the applicaton form
                <br> Admission of students is strictly by the applicantâ€™s age, proven ability and level of maturity at the time of application. Positive past records in former school(s) or college(s) are assets to any applicant
                <br> Complete our e-admission form process in three simple steps.</p>
                <p>1. Click on the image below to download the form in PDF format. <br>2. Print out the form and fill it our clearly and concisely in ink <br> 3.Submit the form with a registration fee of N10,000 to,</p>
                <p>The Principal, <br> The Anwar College<br>23A, Adetokunbo Ademola Road Iyaganku GRA<br>Lagos, Nigeria.</p>
                <p>For directions to the school,<br>Tel: 02-7514579 or 08055114257<br>Email: anwar_college@yahoo.com</p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 admission-form">
                <h3>ADMISSION FORM</h3>
                <div class="inner-content">
                    <p>Please download our Admission Form Below.</p>
                    <a href="images/post-utme.pdf">
                        <img src="images/pdf-img.png" alt="">
                    </a>
                </div>
    
                <div class="inner-content">
                    <p>Please download TVTC FORM below.</p>
                    <a href="images/post-utme.pdf">
                        <img src="images/pdf-img.png" alt="">
                    </a>
                </div>
    
                <div class="inner-content">
                    <p>Download Student Handbook.</p>
                    <a href="images/post-utme.pdf">
                        <img src="images/pdf-img.png" alt="">
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 admission-portal">
                <div class=portal-inner>
                    <h3>ADMISSION PORTAL</h3>
                    <P>Parents can choose to complete all admission process online by using our admission portal here. Please use the form below to get started.</P>
                    <a href="/login"><strong>>> LOGIN HERE</strong></a>
    
                    <div class="">
                        <div class="form-header">
                            <% var obj = errors %>
                            <% if(Object.keys(obj).length === 0){ %>
                                <h3>Register here</h3>
                            <% }else{ %>
                                <h2 class="errors-heading">Oops, please correct the following:</h2>
                                <ul class="errors-list">
                                    <%for(x of obj["errors"]){%>
                                        <li style="color: #CF4A51;"><%= x.msg %> </li>
                                    <%}%>
                                </ul>
                            <% } %>

                            <p style="color: #CF4A51;"><%= mailError %></p>

                            
                        </div>
                        <form class="" action="admission" method="POST" novalidate>
                            <div class="form-field <%= obj.parentName ? 'form-field-invalid' : '' %> ">
                                <input type="text"  name="parentName" class="form-control" placeholder="PARENT NAME" value= "<%= data.parentName%>" >
                                <%for(x in obj["errors"]){%>
                                    <%if(x.param == "parentName"){%>
                                        <p style="color: #CF4A51;"><%= x.param %> <p>
                                    <%}%>
                                    
                                <%}%>
                                
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-field <%= obj.studentName ? 'form-field-invalid' : '' %> ">
                                <input type="text"  name="studentName" class="form-control" placeholder="STUDENT NAME" value="<%= data.studentName%>">
                                
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-field <%= obj.telephone ? 'form-field-invalid' : '' %> ">
                                <input type="text"  name="telephone" class="form-control" placeholder="TELEPHONE" value="<%= data.telephone %>">
                                
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-field <%= obj.email ? 'form-field-invalid' : '' %> ">
                                <input type="email"  aria-describedby="emailHelp" name="email" class="form-control" placeholder="EMAIL" value="<%= data.telephone%>">
                                <small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</small>
                                
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-field <%= errors.password ? 'form-field-invalid' : '' %> ">
                                <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="PASSWORD" value="<%= data.password %>">
                                <%if(errors.password){%>
                                    <div style="color: #CF4A51;" class="error"><%= errors.password.msg %>  </div>
                                <%}%>
                            </div>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block">START REGISTRATION</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <hr>
        <hr>
    </section>
    
    
    <%- include("partials/footer") %>